'''意大利足球甲级联赛足球先生'''（{{lang-it|Migliore calciatore assoluto AIC}}）是[[意大利足球运动员协会|意大利足球运动员协会]]颁发的年度奖项，奖励在上一年[[意大利足球甲级联赛|意大利足球甲级联赛]]表现最好的足球运动员，属[[意甲奥斯卡|意甲最佳]]系列奖项<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.repubblica.it/sport/calcio/2017/01/31/foto/gran_gala_del_calcio_tanti_premiati-157273798/1/#1 | work = [[共和國報|la Repubblica]] | title = Gran Galà del Calcio a Milano: gli juventini i più premiati | date = 2017-01-31 | accessdate = 2022-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200728032752/https://www.repubblica.it/sport/calcio/2017/01/31/foto/gran_gala_del_calcio_tanti_premiati-157273798/1/#1 | archive-date = 2020-07-28 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[尤文图斯足球俱乐部|尤文图斯]]是球员获奖最多的俱乐部，达12次；[[兹拉坦·伊布拉希莫维奇|兹拉坦·伊布拉希莫维奇]]与[[安德烈亚·皮尔洛|安德烈亚·皮尔洛]]均以三次获奖并列第一，其中皮尔洛是连续三年胜出。

== 历史 ==
[[1996年至1997年意大利足球甲级联赛|1996年至1997年意大利足球甲级联赛]]结束后，[[意甲奥斯卡|意甲奥斯卡]]将第一个意大利足球甲级联赛足球先生称号授予[[桑普多利亚足球俱乐部|桑普多利亚足球俱乐部]][[前鋒_(足球)|前锋]][[羅拔圖·文仙尼|羅拔圖·文仙尼]]<ref name=":0">{{Cite web | url = https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/news/james-lawton-mancini-is-failing-to-imbue-city-with-courage-of-winners-2131645.html | work = [[獨立報|The Independent]] | last = Lawton | title = Mancini is failing to imbue City with courage of winners | date = 2010-11-12 | access-date = 2022-01-19 | archive-date = 2020-02-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200204215856/https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/news-and-comment/james-lawton-mancini-is-failing-to-imbue-city-with-courage-of-winners-2131645.html | first = James | dead-url = no}}</ref>。一年后首度为[[国际米兰足球俱乐部|国际米兰]]效力的巴西[[前鋒_(足球)|前锋]][[罗纳尔多|罗纳尔多]]获奖，他在[[1997年至1998年意大利足球甲级联赛|1997至1998年意甲]]进球数排第二，[[1997–98年歐洲足協盃|欧洲足协杯]]第一，为国际米兰夺冠立下汗马功劳<ref name=":1">{{Cite news | dead-url = yes | url = http://www2.raisport.rai.it/news/sport/calcio/199809/22/3607ef0f06e63/ | date = 1998-09-22 | work = Rai Sport | access-date = 2018-06-12 | title = La notte degli Oscar | archive-date = 2018-06-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180612143112/http://www2.raisport.rai.it/news/sport/calcio/199809/22/3607ef0f06e63/}}</ref>。此后两届意甲足球先生分别是[[拉素體育會|拉齐奥俱乐部]]的[[克里斯蒂安·维耶里|克里斯蒂安·维耶里]]<ref name="vieri">{{cite web | url = https://www.footballdatabase.eu/en/player/details/1351-christian-vieri | title = Christian Vieri career stats | publisher = Football Database.eu | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-date = 2021-10-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211009153459/https://www.footballdatabase.eu/en/player/details/1351-christian-vieri | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite news | url = http://www2.raisport.rai.it/news/sport/calcio/199910/05/37fa62f902ab3/ | date = 1999-10-05 | work = Rai Sport | access-date = 2018-12-06 | title = Vieri pigliatutto | archive-date = 2018-12-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181206001908/http://www2.raisport.rai.it/news/sport/calcio/199910/05/37fa62f902ab3/ | dead-url = yes}}</ref>、[[羅馬體育俱樂部|罗马俱乐部]]的[[弗朗切斯科·托蒂|弗朗切斯科·托蒂]]<ref name="totti">{{cite web | url = https://www.footballdatabase.eu/en/player/details/1540-francesco-totti | title = Francesco Totti career stats | publisher = Football Database.eu | access-date = 2022-01-19 | archive-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211121215727/https://www.footballdatabase.eu/en/player/details/1540-francesco-totti | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{Cite news | title = A Francesco Totti l'Oscar del calcio | url = https://www.repubblica.it/online/campionato/oscar/oscar/oscar.html?ref=search | date = 2000-10-02 | work = la Repubblica | access-date = 2022-01-19 | archive-date = 2021-06-06 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210606144926/https://www.repubblica.it/online/campionato/oscar/oscar/oscar.html?ref=search}}</ref>。

[[尤文图斯足球俱乐部|尤文图斯足球俱乐部]]球员[[齐内丁·齐达内|齐内丁·齐达内]]在[[2000年至2001年意大利足球甲级联赛|2000至2001年联赛]]结束后成为法籍意甲足球先生<ref name=":4">{{Cite news | archive-date = 2021-12-30 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.repubblica.it/online/calcio/oscarpar/oscarpar/oscarpar.html | title = Oscar: Zidane batte Totti è lui il più bravo calciatore | date = 2001-10-02 | work = la Repubblica | access-date = 2022-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211230135044/https://www.repubblica.it/online/calcio/oscarpar/oscarpar/oscarpar.html}}</ref>。[[2001年至2002年意大利足球甲级联赛|一年后]]他同在尤文图斯效力的法国同胞[[大卫·特雷泽盖|大卫·特雷泽盖]]获奖，俱乐部还拿下联赛冠军，是足球先生所在俱乐部首次在同赛季夺冠<ref name=":5">{{Cite magazine | date =2018-06-07| title = Le tappe fondamentali e le conquiste | url = https://issuu.com/associazioneitalianacalciatori/docs/aic_il_calciatore_speciale_50mo_web | magazine = Il Calciatore | page = 45 | access-date = 2022-01-19 | archive-date = 2021-12-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211225122649/https://issuu.com/associazioneitalianacalciatori/docs/aic_il_calciatore_speciale_50mo_web | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital02.html | publisher = [[RSSSF|RSSSF.com]] | title = Italy Championship 1998/99 | date = 2003-01-11 | accessdate = 2022-01-19 | archive-date = 2021-03-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210307155423/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital02.html | dead-url = no}}</ref>。第七届足球先生在[[2002年至2003年意大利足球甲级联赛|2002至2003年联赛]]结束后颁发，尤文图斯再度夺冠，该队来自捷克的[[中场|中场]][[帕维尔·内德维德|帕维尔·内德维德]]与弗朗切斯科·托蒂并列当选，是意甲足球先生至今唯一的双黄蛋<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital03.html | publisher = RSSSF.com | title = Italy Championship 1998/99 | date = 2003-08-31 | accessdate = 2022-01-19 | archive-date = 2021-12-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211207092241/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital03.html | dead-url = no}}</ref>，托蒂成为首位双获足球先生的运动员，是该赛季罗马俱乐部头号射手<ref name=":6">{{Cite news | url = https://ricerca.gelocal.it/tribunatreviso/archivio/tribunatreviso/2004/01/13/VS1TC_VS103.html | title = L'"Oscar" Aic a Totti e Nedved | date = 2004-01-13 | work = La Tribuna di Treviso | access-date = 2022-01-20 | archive-date = 2021-06-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210606144935/https://ricerca.gelocal.it/tribunatreviso/archivio/tribunatreviso/2004/01/13/VS1TC_VS103.html | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="totti" />。[[2003年至2004年意大利足球甲级联赛|2003至2004年]]首度为[[AC米兰|AC米兰]]效力的[[卡卡|卡卡]]入选<ref name=":7">{{Cite news | url = https://www.repubblica.it/2005/a/sezioni/sport/calcio/serie_a/5premi/5premi/5premi.html | title = Oscar Aic, rossoneri superstar Kakà e gli altri, 2004 da ricordare |date=24 January 2005 | work = la Repubblica | access-date = 2022-01-20 | archive-date = 2020-10-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201021012042/https://www.repubblica.it/2005/a/sezioni/sport/calcio/serie_a/5premi/5premi/5premi.html | dead-url = no}}</ref>。[[2004年至2005年意大利足球甲级联赛|2004至2005年]]得主[[阿尔贝托·吉拉迪诺|阿尔贝托·吉拉迪诺]]联赛期间打入24球，其中[[附加賽|附加賽]]的致胜球挽救[[帕爾馬足球會|帕尔玛足球俱乐部]]免遭降级[[意大利足球乙级联赛|意乙联赛]]<ref name="gilardino">{{cite web | url = https://www.footballdatabase.eu/en/player/details/1468-alberto-gilardino | title = Alberto Gilardino career stats | publisher = Football Database.eu | access-date = 2022-01-20 | archive-date = 2021-11-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211112051052/https://www.footballdatabase.eu/en/player/details/1468-alberto-gilardino | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name=":8">{{Cite news | archive-date = 2019-05-18 | url = https://www.gazzetta.it/Calcio/SerieA/Primo_Piano/2006/01_Gennaio/23/pezzoscar.shtml | title = Oscar, solo Gilardino e Juve | date = 2006-01-23 | work = [[米蘭體育報|La Gazzetta dello Sport]] | access-date = 2022-01-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190518191552/https://www.gazzetta.it/Calcio/SerieA/Primo_Piano/2006/01_Gennaio/23/pezzoscar.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

[[法比奥·卡纳瓦罗|法比奥·卡纳瓦罗]]在[[2005年至2006年意大利足球甲级联赛|2005至2006年联赛]]结束后成为首位获奖后卫<ref name=":9">{{Cite news | url = https://ricerca.repubblica.it/repubblica/archivio/repubblica/2007/01/30/buffon-oggi-la-juve-poi-pensero-al.html?ref=search | title = Buffon: Oggi la Juve poi penserò al resto | date = 2007-01-30 | work = la Repubblica | access-date = 2022-01-20 | archive-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210712020249/https://ricerca.repubblica.it/repubblica/archivio/repubblica/2007/01/30/buffon-oggi-la-juve-poi-pensero-al.html?ref=search | dead-url = no}}</ref>，[[2006年意大利足球醜聞|2006年意大利足球醜聞]]爆发后尤文图斯成绩取消并降级意乙<ref>{{cite news | dead-url = no | url = http://download.ju29ro.com/sentenze/Calciopoli_-_Sentenza_Caf_(14_luglio_2006).pdf | title = Testo della decisione relativa al Comm. Uff. N. 1/C – Riunione del 29 giugno / 3 - 4 - 5 - 6 - 7 luglio 2006 | publisher = Commissione d'Appello Federale – Federazione Italiana Giuoco Calcio | page = 58 | date = 2006-07-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211030184450/http://download.ju29ro.com/sentenze/Calciopoli_-_Sentenza_Caf_(14_luglio_2006).pdf | archive-date = 2021-10-30 | access-date = 2022-01-20 | format = PDF}}</ref>，他改签[[皇家马德里足球俱乐部|皇家马德里足球俱乐部]]后还拿下[[國際足協世界足球先生|國際足協世界足球先生]]<ref>{{cite web | access-date = 2022-01-20 | url = https://www.fifa.com/news/cannavaro-stands-alone-amid-attacking-dominance-2854124 | title = Cannavaro stands alone amid attacking dominance | publisher = [[国际足球联合会|FIFA]] | archive-date = 2016-03-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305093022/http://www.fifa.com/ballon-dor/news/y=2015/m=10/news=cannavaro-stands-alone-amid-attacking-dominance-2720898.html | dead-url = no | date = 2015-10-23}}</ref>和[[金球奖_(足球)|金球奖]]<ref>{{cite web | archive-date = 2022-01-20 | url = https://www.theguardian.com/football/2006/nov/28/newsstory.sport1 | title = Cannavaro only third defender to win coveted Ballon d'Or | work = [[衛報|The Guardian]] | date = 2006-11-27 | access-date = 2022-01-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211214035431/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2006/nov/28/newsstory.sport1 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Agreements with the Spanish club Real Madrid CF | archive-date = 2010-11-17 | url = http://www.juventus.com/site/filesite/finance/comunicatipricesensitive/27_lug_2006_eng.pdf | publisher = [[尤文图斯足球俱乐部|juventus.com]] | date = 2006-07-27 | access-date = 2010-11-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101117055705/http://www.juventus.com/site/filesite/finance/comunicatipricesensitive/27_lug_2006_eng.pdf}}</ref>。卡卡[[2006年至2007年意大利足球甲级联赛|一年后]]再次获奖并拿下国际足联世界足球先生，距他上次获奖还只过去三年<ref name=":10">{{Cite news | url = https://ricerca.repubblica.it/repubblica/archivio/repubblica/2008/01/29/sto-bene-il-mio-sogno-sempre-la.html?ref=search | title = Sto bene e il mio sogno è sempre la Champions League | date = 2008-01-29 | work = la Repubblica | access-date = 2022-01-20 | archive-date = 2020-08-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200810063316/https://ricerca.repubblica.it/repubblica/archivio/repubblica/2008/01/29/sto-bene-il-mio-sogno-sempre-la.html?ref=search | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

[[兹拉坦·伊布拉希莫维奇|兹拉坦·伊布拉希莫维奇]]接下来连夺两次意甲足球先生，带领国际米兰两度折桂<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital08.html | publisher = RSSSF.com | title = Italy Championship 2007/08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210830084111/http://rsssf.com/tablesi/ital08.html | accessdate = 2022-01-20 | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-08-30 | date = 2009-08-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | archive-date = 2021-10-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211030202452/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital09.html | date = 2009-08-12 | url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital09.html | publisher = RSSSF.com | title = Italy Championship 2008/09 | accessdate = 2022-01-20 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name=":11">{{Cite news | url = https://ricerca.repubblica.it/repubblica/archivio/repubblica/2009/01/20/ibrahimovic-il-migliore-per-colleghi.html?ref=search | title = È Ibrahimovic il migliore per i colleghi | date = 2010-01-20 | work = la Repubblica | access-date = 2022-01-20 | archive-date = 2020-11-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201128200956/https://ricerca.repubblica.it/repubblica/archivio/repubblica/2009/01/20/ibrahimovic-il-migliore-per-colleghi.html?ref=search | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name=":12">{{Cite news | url = https://www.repubblica.it/sport/calcio/2010/01/19/news/gli_oscar_dell_aic_ibra_de_rossi_mou-2005797/?ref=search | title = Gli Oscar dell'Aic Ibra, De Rossi, Mou | date = 2010-01-19 | work = la Repubblica | access-date = 2022-01-20 | archive-date = 2020-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200923011626/https://www.repubblica.it/sport/calcio/2010/01/19/news/gli_oscar_dell_aic_ibra_de_rossi_mou-2005797/?ref=search | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[2008年至2009年意大利足球甲級聯賽|2008至2009年联赛]]他还拿下[[意大利足球四级联赛最佳射手|最佳射手]]，是首位同时囊括意甲最佳射手和足球先生的球员<ref>{{cite web | url = https://us.soccerway.com/national/italy/serie-a/2008-2009/regular-season/r6999/ | title = Serie A 2008/2009 | publisher = soccerway.com | access-date = 2022-01-20 | archive-date = 2021-09-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210913003437/https://us.soccerway.com/national/italy/serie-a/2008-2009/regular-season/r6999/ | dead-url = no}}</ref>。伊布拉希莫维奇在[[2009年至2010年意大利足球甲級聯賽|2009至2010年联赛]]开始前离开国际米兰加入[[巴塞罗那足球俱乐部|巴塞罗那足球俱乐部]]，[[迪亞高·米列圖|迪亞高·米列圖]]上位后以赛季进球总数第二带领国际米兰夺冠并拿下足球先生<ref>{{cite web | url = https://ca.soccerway.com/national/italy/serie-a/2009-2010/regular-season/r9194/ | title = Serie A 2009/2010 | publisher = soccerway.com | access-date = 2022-01-20 | archive-date = 2021-11-02 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211102170408/https://ca.soccerway.com/national/italy/serie-a/2009-2010/regular-season/r9194/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital2010.html | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211106003723/http://rsssf.com/tablesi/ital2010.html | publisher = RSSSF.com | title = Italy Championship 2009/10 | date = 2013-02-07 | accessdate = 2022-01-20 | archive-date = 2021-11-06}}</ref><ref name=":13">{{cite news | last = Graffeo | first = Vito | title = Vincitori Oscar del Calcio 2010 | url = http://www.sportlive.it/calcio/vincitori-e-premi-oscar-del-calcio-2010.html | access-date = 2015-12-22 | work = SportLive.it | date = 2011-01-24 | archive-date = 2015-12-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222121654/http://www.sportlive.it/calcio/vincitori-e-premi-oscar-del-calcio-2010.html | dead-url = yes}}</ref>。[[2010年至2011年意大利足球甲級聯賽|下一年]]AC米兰借回伊布拉希莫维奇，他又一次带领球队夺冠并第三次当选足球先生<ref>{{Cite web| url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital2011.html | publisher = RSSSF.com | title = Italy Championship 2010/11 | date = 2009-08-12 | accessdate = 2022-01-20 | archive-date = 2021-03-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210302234111/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital2011.html | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name=":14">{{cite news | title = Gran Gala' AIC 2011/ Ibra miglior giocatore, El Sharaawy giovane della B, ecco tutti i vincitori | url = https://www.ilsussidiario.net/news/calcio-e-altri-sport/milan/2012/1/24/gran-gala-aic-2011-ibra-miglior-giocatore-el-shaarawy-giovane-della-b-ecco-tutti-i-vincitori/235131/ | access-date = 2022-01-20 | work = IlSussidiario.net | date = 2012-01-24 | archive-date = 2021-12-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211221112336/https://www.ilsussidiario.net/news/calcio-e-altri-sport/milan/2012/1/24/gran-gala-aic-2011-ibra-miglior-giocatore-el-shaarawy-giovane-della-b-ecco-tutti-i-vincitori/235131/ | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

[[安德烈亚·皮尔洛|安德烈亚·皮尔洛]][[2011年至2012年意大利足球甲級聯賽|2011至2012年联赛]]从国际米兰转会尤文图斯，连续三年获封足球先生并带领球队夺冠，追平伊布拉希莫维奇的纪录<ref name=":15">{{cite news | dead-url = yes | archive-date = 2013-05-11 | url = http://www.tuttosport.com/calcio/serie_a/2013/01/27-242192/Gran+Gal& | title = Gran Galà del Calcio Aic. E' Pirlo il migliore del 2012 | work = [[都灵体育报|Tuttosport]] | date = 2013-01-27 | access-date = 2013-05-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130511222058/http://www.tuttosport.com/calcio/serie_a/2013/01/27-242192/Gran+Gal%26 }}</ref><ref name=":16">{{cite news | work = La Gazzetta dello Sport | access-date = 2022-01-20 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.gazzetta.it/Calcio/27-01-2014/calcio-gran-gala-miglior-portiere-handanovic-202224603209.shtml | title = Calcio, Gran Galà. Pirlo giocatore dell'anno: "Consiglio Totti a Prandelli" | archive-date = 2020-10-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201020231858/https://www.gazzetta.it/Calcio/27-01-2014/calcio-gran-gala-miglior-portiere-handanovic-202224603209.shtml | date = 2014-01-27}}</ref><ref name=":17">{{cite news | url = http://www.corrieredellosport.it/calcio/serie_a/2014/12/15-388238/Serie+A,+'Gran+Gal%C3%A0+del+calcio'.+Segui+l'evento+LIVE | title = Serie A, 'Gran Galà del calcio': trionfa la Juve | work = Corriere dello Sport | date = 2014-12-15 | access-date = 2016-03-04 | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304105720/http://www.corrieredellosport.it/calcio/serie_a/2014/12/15-388238/Serie+A%2C+%27Gran+Gal%C3%A0+del+calcio%27.+Segui+l%27evento+LIVE | archive-date = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。他在第一个联赛就助攻上百次，完成传球2643次，传球完成率高达八成七，比其他球员至少多五百余次，同年全世界只有[[哈維|哈維]]完成传球次数超过皮尔洛<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.si.com/soccer/2012/05/03/pirlo | title = Andrea Pirlo still as good as ever | work = [[運動畫刊|Sports Illustrated]] | author = Adam Digby | access-date = 2022-01-20 | archive-date = 2020-11-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201126191452/https://www.si.com/soccer/2012/05/03/pirlo | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.tuttojuve.com/primo-piano/elogio-di-pirlo-su-sports-illustrated-tutto-merito-di-baggio-93031 | title = Elogio di Pirlo su Sports Illustrated: tutto merito di... Baggio | publisher = tuttojuve.com | author1 = Sandro Scarpa | date = 2012-05-04 | access-date = 2022-01-20 | archive-date = 2021-11-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211115064335/https://www.tuttojuve.com/primo-piano/elogio-di-pirlo-su-sports-illustrated-tutto-merito-di-baggio-93031 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。一年后，[[卡洛斯·特维斯|卡洛斯·特维斯]]在尤文图斯队的[[2014年至2015年意大利足球甲級聯賽|最后一个赛季]]攻入20球，登顶俱乐部射手榜并入选足球先生<ref name=":18">{{cite news | last = Riggio | first = Salvatore | title = Gran Galà del Calcio: è dominio Juve, miglior squadra e miglior allenatore | url = https://www.sportmediaset.mediaset.it/calcio/calcio/gran-gala-del-calcio-e-dominio-juve-miglior-squadra-e-miglior-allenatore_1084196-201502a.shtml | access-date = 2022-01-20 | work = Sport Mediaset | date = 2015-12-14 | archive-date = 2021-04-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210415015945/https://www.sportmediaset.mediaset.it/calcio/calcio/gran-gala-del-calcio-e-dominio-juve-miglior-squadra-e-miglior-allenatore_1084196-201502a.shtml | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://int.soccerway.com/national/italy/serie-a/20142015/regular-season/r27139/ | title = Serie A 2014/2015 | publisher = soccerway.com | access-date = 2022-01-20 | archive-date = 2021-04-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210430190203/https://int.soccerway.com/national/italy/serie-a/20142015/regular-season/r27139/ | dead-url = no}}</ref>。[[2015年至2016年意大利足球甲级联赛|2015至2016年联赛]]后获奖的[[莱昂纳多·博努奇|莱昂纳多·博努奇]]又是尤文图斯球员，还是史上第二名获此殊荣的后卫<ref name=":19">{{cite web | url = https://www.corriere.it/foto-gallery/sport/17_gennaio_31/gran-gala-calcio-juventus-fa-incetta-premi-serie-a-c6dc644c-e795-11e6-8168-2d40923ac04f.shtml | title = Gran Galà del calcio, la Juventus fa incetta di premi | work = [[晚邮报|Il Corriere della Sera]] | date = 2017-01-31 | access-date = 2022-01-20 | archive-date = 2021-10-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211027194818/https://www.corriere.it/foto-gallery/sport/17_gennaio_31/gran-gala-calcio-juventus-fa-incetta-premi-serie-a-c6dc644c-e795-11e6-8168-2d40923ac04f.shtml | dead-url = no}}</ref>。[[2016年至2017年意大利足球甲级联赛|下一届联赛]]获奖的[[詹路易吉·布冯|詹路易吉·布冯]]仍属尤文图斯队，是首位足球先生守门员<ref name=":20">{{Cite web | url = https://football-italia.net/buffon-named-best-player/ | title = Buffon named best player | date = 2017-11-27 | publisher = Football Italia | access-date = 2022-01-20 | archive-date = 2021-12-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211228171710/https://football-italia.net/buffon-named-best-player/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。尤文图斯以六连冠创下意甲历史纪录之际，布冯追平[[维尔吉尼奥·罗塞塔|维尔吉尼奥·罗塞塔]]、[[乔瓦尼·费拉里|乔瓦尼·费拉里]]、[[朱塞佩·弗里诺|朱塞佩·弗里诺]]的八次联赛冠军球员纪录<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.goal.com/it/notizie/giocatori-pluriscudettati-buffon-raggiunge-la-vetta-con-8/xnk18vgwb73c1xgwrr10bgj4a | title = Giocatori pluriscudettati, Buffon raggiunge la vetta con 8: Bonucci a 7 | publisher = [[Goal.com|Goal]] | date = 2017-05-21 | access-date = 2022-01-20 | archive-date = 2021-03-01 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210301114103/https://www.goal.com/it/notizie/giocatori-pluriscudettati-buffon-raggiunge-la-vetta-con-8/xnk18vgwb73c1xgwrr10bgj4a }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.espn.com/soccer/italian-serie-a/story/3130448/juventus-clinch-sixth-consecutive-serie-a-title-against-crotone | title = Juventus Clinch Sixth Consecutive Serie A Title Against Crotone | work = ESPN FC | date = 2017-05-21 | access-date = 2022-01-20 | archive-date = 2021-12-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211220175749/https://www.espn.com/soccer/italian-serie-a/story/3130448/juventus-clinch-sixth-consecutive-serie-a-title-against-crotone | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.juventus.com/en/news/articles/juventus-champions-of-italy-for-the-sixth-time-in-a-row | title = Juventus, Champions of Italy for the sixth time in a row | publisher = juventus.com | date = 2017-05-21 | access-date = 2022-01-20 | archive-date = 2021-05-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210516160212/https://www.juventus.com/en/news/articles/juventus-champions-of-italy-for-the-sixth-time-in-a-row | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

国际米兰球员[[毛罗·伊卡尔迪|毛罗·伊卡尔迪]]拿下[[2017年至2018年意大利足球甲级联赛|2017至2018年联赛]]足球先生奖，终结尤文图斯队选手六连胜<ref name=":21">{{Cite web | url = https://sport.sky.it/calcio/serie-a/2018/12/03/gran-gala-del-calcio-aic-2018-premiati | title = Gran Galà del calcio AIC 2018: Icardi il miglior giocatore 2017-2018. Tutti i premi | date = 2018-12-03 | publisher = Sky Sport | access-date = 2022-01-20 | archive-date = 2021-11-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211110190515/https://sport.sky.it/calcio/serie-a/2018/12/03/gran-gala-del-calcio-aic-2018-premiati | dead-url = no }}</ref>，他与拉齐奥球员[[奇罗·因莫比莱|奇罗·因莫比莱]]以29球并列本届联赛最佳射手<ref>{{cite web | url = https://ca.soccerway.com/national/italy/serie-a/20172018/regular-season/r42011/ | title = Serie A 2017/2018 | publisher = soccerway.com | access-date = 2022-01-20 | archive-date = 2021-11-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211128155353/https://ca.soccerway.com/national/italy/serie-a/20172018/regular-season/r42011/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但拿下联赛冠军的仍是尤文图斯<ref>{{Cite web | accessdate = 2022-01-20 | url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital2018.html | publisher = RSSSF.com | title = Italy Championship 2017/18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210922200440/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital2018.html | archive-date = 2021-09-22 | date = 2021-01-14 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。此后尤文图斯的[[基斯坦奴·朗拿度|基斯坦奴·朗拿度]]连续两年当选足球先生，他在[[2018年至2019年意大利足球甲级联赛|2018至2019年赛季]]从皇家马德里转会尤文图斯，一亿美元转会费[[最高足球轉會費列表|刷新意大利足球俱乐部纪录]]<ref>{{cite web | title = Cristiano Ronaldo signs for Juventus! | url = https://www.juventus.com/en/news/articles/cristiano-ronaldo-signs-for-juventus | publisher = juventus.com | date = 2018-07-10 | access-date = 2022-01-20 | archive-date = 2021-12-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211210012640/https://www.juventus.com/en/news/articles/cristiano-ronaldo-signs-for-juventus | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=":22">{{Cite web | dead-url = yes | url = https://www.football-italia.net/147170/ronaldo-crowned-serie-best-player | title = Ronaldo crowned Serie A best player | date = 2019-12-02 | publisher = Football Italia | access-date = 2021-04-14 | archive-date = 2021-04-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210414113425/https://www.football-italia.net/147170/ronaldo-crowned-serie-best-player }}</ref>。[[2019年至2020年意大利足球甲级联赛|2019至2020年联赛]]他以31枚进球位居尤文图斯榜首，排在联赛第二<ref name=":23">{{Cite web | url = https://www.football-italia.net/167974/gran-gal%C3%A0-del-calcio-winners | date = 2021-03-19 | publisher = Football Italia | access-date = 2021-05-16 | archive-date = 2021-05-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210516065055/https://www.football-italia.net/167974/gran-gal%C3%A0-del-calcio-winners | title = Gran Galà del Calcio: The winners | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://ca.soccerway.com/national/italy/serie-a/20192020/regular-season/r54890/ | title = Serie A 2019/2020 | publisher = soccerway.com | access-date = 2022-01-20 | archive-date = 2021-05-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210510004834/https://ca.soccerway.com/national/italy/serie-a/20192020/regular-season/r54890/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

